net.proteusframework.internet.servlet.filter

Class ClientLog4JFilter

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.proteusframework.internet.servlet.filter.ClientLog4JFilter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javax.servlet.Filter

    public class ClientLog4JFilter
extends java.lang.Object
implements javax.servlet.Filter
    Log4J filter. This filter can be used by client side code to log messages on the server. Matching requests are not chained unless specifically directed to. The log message, level, and exception are placed in the body of the request. The current log level is returned. See logger.js.
    Author:
    Russ Tennant (russ@proteus.co), Pat Double (double@i2rd.com) (put into servlet library)
